      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STORMY DAY (6) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 5.5 lengths at this track in a handy 22.16 beating Breaker Of Rules. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. The hardest to beat again. MINNIE'S MY MUM (1) boasts a strong record this journey here with five wins and four minors from 12 tries. Scored by 0.8 lengths last time (30.22) in a OPEN over 512m at Mt Gambier. Looks a key chance on best figures. IS HE LUCKY (2) missed the frame over 350m at Healesville latest but ran a handy 19.35 when beaten 2.75 lengths. Rates a leading chance if runs up to latest. CANYA NAMELESS (3) was strongly fancied last time on the back of some good form but finished second (22.40) at this track. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Well placed and gets her chance.",
